WEBVTT

00:00.337 --> 00:01.737
Previously on The Fosters... 

00:01.822 --> 00:04.290
I gave the money to Ana
so she'd change her story.

00:04.340 --> 00:07.275
- You bribed her?
- I'll tell the DA.

00:07.309 --> 00:10.378
- I want $10,000.
- That freaking woman. I could kill her.

00:10.412 --> 00:12.714
You are gonna stay as far away
from that woman as possible.

00:12.748 --> 00:16.518
You saw Ana Gutierrez in an argument
the night that she went missing?

00:16.552 --> 00:19.554
- Is this the guy?
- Yeah, this is the guy.

00:19.588 --> 00:24.259
- Donald isn't my dad?
- Not according to the birth certificate.

00:24.293 --> 00:26.394
It says Robert Quinn?

00:26.428 --> 00:28.730
[man] Until there is signed
consent from Robert Quinn,

00:28.764 --> 00:31.924
the adoption of Callie Jacob is denied.

00:32.188 --> 00:34.546
Told you I was gonna hit you where it hurt.

00:39.547 --> 00:41.117
[Doctor] Your bones are
shattered in several places.

00:41.343 --> 00:44.245
- He's gonna need surgery.
- He's a pianist.

00:44.279 --> 00:47.148
Our concern right now is making
sure he can still use it at all.

00:49.000 --> 00:55.074
